Name of group - multi-academy trust (MAT) or school sponsor. Where there is more than a single MAT set up by a school sponsor, the performance data is calculated based on all of the schools in the MATs and single academy trusts set up by the school sponsor. Where there is only a single MAT set up by a school sponsor, performance data is calculated for the MAT.
